wl1251: configure hardware en-/decryption for monitor mode

Disable hardware encryption (DF_ENCRYPTION_DISABLE) and decryption
(DF_SNIFF_MODE_ENABLE) via wl1251_acx_feature_cfg while monitor interface is
present.

